      "text": "Kiosk Tablet #1\n(Android · Kotlin · Compose)\n\n• Mic / Touchscreen\n• Sherpa-ONNX STT (Zipformer / Whisper)\n• STT post-proc + intonation\n• Emergency Detector (Tier 1/2 + SOS)\n• Sherpa-ONNX TTS (VITS)",
