      "locked": false,
      "text": "SQLite (single file)\n\n• kb_articles (1k–5k / shelter)\n• kb_embeddings (MiniLM)\n• query_logs · feedback_logs\n• article_biases (RLHF)\n• evac_config · shelters\n• emergencies · messages\n• users · kiosks\n\nModels prewarmed at startup:\nMiniLM · NLLB-200 · Ollama\n(Llama 3.2 + TranslateGemma)",
