      "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "INPUTS  →  voice (16 kHz · 1.5s pre-buffer) · text fallback · touch (clarification chips · SOS) · admin console forms\nPROCESSING  →  100% local AI on shelter LAN — Sherpa-ONNX (STT/TTS) · NLLB-200 (translation) · MiniLM (embeddings + intent) · BM25 + RRF (hybrid retrieval) · Ollama (Llama 3.2 rewriter · TranslateGemma formatter)\nOUTPUTS  →  spoken answer (TTS · ~2.1s e2e) · chat-bubble text · clarification chips · emergency alert · structured query log",
